    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Looks really good.\r\n\r\nit's still not a real browser, so still not as close as what we ship to the end user but will definitely catch a lot of bugs!\r\n\r\nI see there is a certain level of compatibility with react and vue. It'd be be nice to check we can reach the same level of feature coverage in every flavour we have. \r\nThere is nothing for angular but maybe we can work something out with puppeteer or cypress.\r\n\r\n",
