  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Last year, I took this class from Kent C. Dodds.\r\n\r\nLucky you! I'd love to take that class. :slightly_smiling_face: \r\n\r\nWe can also test directly the production build with the integration tests (tested it [here](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/pull/3931/commits/5d91e78f7fbfb2eda8be7bf491d3e64adb8a9111)) but we need to see how to make it works with tests running during development.\r\n\r\nAgree for E2E tests, but it asks more efforts to be put in place so I see it more like a second step to do after the integration tests. \r\n",
